## Workflow Summary

For each new job opportunity, the full loop is:

```
Find role → 60-second filter → Add to Notion (Status: Bookmarked)
→ Read JD → Fit score → Update Notion (Status: Applying)
→ Adapt CV → Write cover letter (if priority) → Research company
→ Submit application → Update Notion (Status: Applied, set Applied Date)
→ Log contacts, next action, notes as process unfolds
```

